titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on 3-bromo-1-(3-chloro-2-pyridinyl)-1H-pyrazole-5-carboxylic acid (CAS No. 500011-86-9).

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary:
12/13/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on 3-bromo-1-(3-chloro-2-pyridinyl)-1H-pyrazole-5-carboxylic acid (CAS No. 500011-86-9).
